---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service" description="Terms governing your use of Tangle Technologies, Inc.'s SaaS products and APIs.">

  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-32 pb-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mb-16">Effective: April 27, 2026 · Last updated: April 27, 2026</p>

    <div class="space-y-12 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed text-[15px]">

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing or using the services provided by Tangle Technologies, Inc. ("Tangle," "we," "us," or "our"), including our websites (tangle.tools, app.tangle.tools, ai.tangle.tools, cloud.tangle.tools), APIs, and related services (collectively, the "Services"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service ("Terms"). If you do not agree, do not use the Services.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-4">2. Description of Services</h2>
        <p>Tangle provides AI-powered development tools, cloud sandboxes, deployment infrastructure, and related services for software development.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-4">3. Eligibility</h2>
        <p>You must be at least 18 years old and have the legal capacity to enter into these Terms. By using the Services, you represent that you meet these requirements.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-4">4. Account Registration</h2>
        <p>You may need to create an account to use certain features. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your credentials and for all activities under your account. Notify us immediately at <a href="mailto:hello@tangle.tools" class="underline">hello@tangle.tools</a> if you suspect unauthorized access.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-4">5. Acceptable Use</h2>
        <p>You agree not to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mt-2">
          <li>Violate any applicable law or regulation.</li>
          <li>Infringe on intellectual property rights.</li>
          <li>Transmit malware or malicious code.</li>
          <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems.</li>
          <li>Use the Services to harm, harass, or defraud others.</li>
          <li>Reverse-engineer or decompile the Services (except as permitted by law).</li>
          <li>Use the Services for cryptocurrency mining without authorization.</li>
          <li>Overload or disrupt the Services.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-4">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-text-primary mt-4 mb-2">Your content</h3>
        <p>You retain ownership of content you create using the Services. You grant Tangle a limited license to host, store, and process your content solely to provide the Services.</p>
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-text-primary mt-4 mb-2">Our content</h3>
        <p>The Services, including software, documentation, and branding, are owned by Tangle and protected by intellectual property laws.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-4">7. Payment and Billing</h2>
        <p>Certain Services require payment. Fees are described on our pricing page. All fees are non-refundable except as required by law or stated in a specific service agreement.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-4">8. Service Availability</h2>
        <p>We strive for high availability but do not guarantee uninterrupted service. Scheduled maintenance will be communicated in advance when feasible.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-4">9. Data and Privacy</h2>
        <p>Your use of the Services is subject to our <a href="/privacy-policy/" class="underline">Privacy Policy</a>. You are responsible for any data you upload or process through the Services. The runtime redactor scrubs credentials, payment-card numbers, and government identifiers from outbound model-vendor calls and our internal logs before transmission; see the Privacy Policy for full detail.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-4">10. Termination</h2>
        <p>We may suspend or terminate your account for violation of these Terms. You may close your account at any time by contacting <a href="mailto:hello@tangle.tools" class="underline">hello@tangle.tools</a>. Upon termination, your data will be handled per our Data Retention and Disposal Policy.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-4">11. Limitation of Liability</h2>
